CERT-UA alert: https://cert.gov.ua/article/6281076
Why mapped: Vendor reports confirm delivery via targeted spear-phish emails containing signed .rdp attachments impersonating
vendors and Microsoft. See CERT-UA alerts listing campaign waves and sample screenshots. Recommended data sources: Mail gateway logs, EML archive, attachment hashes, DKIM/SPF/DMARC.
